  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Repeated Dose, Active Control Drug, Parallel-group and Single-center Phase I Study of the Safety of Intravenous Administration of NI-071 in Comparison With Remicade® in Japanese Patients With Rheumatoid Arthritis Inadequately Treated With Methotrexate</official_title>
